- Download the official Raspbian from the foundation
- Run https://github.com/DexterInd/Raspbian_For_Robots/blob/master/jessie_update/jessie-heavy-upgrade.sh
on that image
- Manually start tightvncserver
- Enter robots1234 password when required
- Run these two lines:
    https://github.com/DexterInd/Raspbian_For_Robots/blob/master/jessie_update/tightvncserver.sh#L23-L24
  sudo systemctl enable vncserver@1.service
  sudo systemctl start vncserver@1.service
- Manually start novnc:
  sudo systemctl enable novnc.service
  sudo systemctl start novnc.service
Reboot and check that VNC, noVNC, Shellinabox are all fine
Run DI_Update
Start piclone and clone card onto a 4Gig Sandisk card
- enable Pi Camera

